{"tid":1802191,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"四月挪威行程","createTime":"2019-12-29T09:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T17:24:14.000Z","uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7d7f89d322756f71680f908da53b30c18b52fc","tid":1802191,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"我四月初去挪威大約十日<br />\n先係Bergen 落機，之後係Oslo 上機返香港<br />\n已經知道Geirangerfjorden and Hardangerfjord 係唔開，只係開松恩峽灣 Sognefjord &amp; 呂瑟峽灣 Lysefjorden，所以應該會去哂呢兩個地方<br />\n仲有冇其他建議呢？<br />\n聽講Lofoten 好靚，但係好遠呀，仲要搭內陸機去，其實景色係咪同Bergen 差唔多呢？"},{"pid":"22bf1460a0fa3d9ab51a88c7bd770f0add118a4a","tid":1802191,"uid":259021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"LM ... 8 月會去北歐 90 日"},{"pid":"165522dfb8efa51bef9ac787fa4f712d260c668f","tid":1802191,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22bf1460a0fa3d9ab51a88c7bd770f0add118a4a","tid":1802191,"uid":259021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"LM ... 8 月會去北歐 90 日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"諗住洗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好豪"},{"pid":"5c0073e180c789250b3083c65c4cd62d560c6219","tid":1802191,"uid":39102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22bf1460a0fa3d9ab51a88c7bd770f0add118a4a","tid":1802191,"uid":259021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"LM ... 8 月會去北歐 90 日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}